title: Eraserheads - Anthology Two
description:
The Eraserheads are a Filipino rock band formed at around '89, making hits such as 'Pare Ko', 'Ang Huling El Bimbo' and 'Toyang', among others. They are considered to have shaped the face of Pinoy Rock, and many people refer to them as 'The Philippine Beatles' due to their distinct style and various love songs.

This is the second of the Anthology series, it only has 28 songs.
